# Cursor Rules for ATHÅ¸RE Project

## Project Type
Shopify 2.0 Theme (converted from React)

## Primary Working Directory
`athyre-theme/` - All active development

## Language & Framework
- Liquid (Shopify templating)
- Vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)
- CSS (custom utilities, no Tailwind in production)

## Code Style

### Liquid
- Use `{%- -%}` for whitespace control
- Comment with `{%- comment -%}`
- Use `| t` filter for all user-facing strings
- Prefer `{% render %}` over `{% include %}`

### CSS
- BEM naming: `.block__element--modifier`
- Section scoping: `.section-{{ section.id }}`
- Mobile-first media queries
- No !important unless absolutely necessary

### JavaScript
- Vanilla JS only, no jQuery
- Use `data-*` attributes for DOM selection
- Dispatch custom events for state changes
- Always handle loading/error states

## File Patterns

### New Section
```liquid
<section class="section-name section-{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="container">
    {%- comment -%} Content {%- endcomment -%}
  </div>
</section>

{% style %}
  .section-{{ section.id }} { }
{% endstyle %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Section Name",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
```

### New Snippet
```liquid
{%- comment -%}
  Snippet: snippet-name
  Usage: {% render 'snippet-name', param: value %}
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="snippet-name">
  {{ param }}
</div>
```

## Key Files
- `layout/theme.liquid` - Main wrapper
- `assets/base.css` - All styles
- `assets/theme.js` - All JavaScript
- `locales/en.default.json` - Translations
- `config/settings_schema.json` - Theme settings

## Don't
- Don't use React/Vue/Angular
- Don't add npm dependencies to theme
- Don't use Tailwind classes (use custom utilities)
- Don't hardcode text (use translations)
- Don't forget section schemas

## Do
- Use Shopify AJAX API for cart
- Add translations for new strings
- Update UPDATES.md for changes
- Test on mobile
- Check with `shopify theme check`

